BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (In today's fast-growing food delivery landscape, customers often struggle to quickly find and order their) Tj T* (desired meals. Browsing large menus, customizing orders, and checking cart totals can be) Tj T* (time-consuming. The Online Food Ordering Assistant Chatbot is an intelligent virtual assistant designed to) Tj T* (simplify and enhance the food ordering experience.) Tj T* ET
Q
