q
0 0 0 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (This project focuses on developing a dynamic chatbot integrated directly into a food dashboard. Instead of) Tj T* (manually browsing the menu, users can interact with the chatbot using natural language queries such as) Tj T* ("Add a burger" or "Show me the menu." The chatbot interprets user intent and adds items to the cart,) Tj T* (displays the current cart total, and processes checkout in real time.) Tj T* ET
Q
