q
0 0 0 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 50 Tm /F1 10 Tf 15 TL (The system uses a structured menu dataset containing attributes like item name, price, and image. By) Tj T* (applying rule-based keyword-based Natural Language Processing \(NLP\), the chatbot identifies user) Tj T* (requests and responds accordingly. It handles follow-up queries, enabling a smooth conversational) Tj T* (ordering experience similar to interacting with a human food counter assistant.) Tj T* ET
Q
